Module chav1961.purelib
Package chav1961.purelib.streams.interfaces.intern

Interface MarkUpOutputWriter<Terminals extends java.lang.Enum<?>,​SectionState extends java.lang.Enum<?>,​SectionActions extends java.lang.Enum<?>,​FontState extends java.lang.Enum<?>,​FontActions extends java.lang.Enum<?>,​Parameter>

Type Parameters:
Terminals - terminal of FSM
FontState - current state of font changing FSM
SectionState - current state of section changing FSM
FontActions - font actions for given font changing FSM
SectionActions - section actions for given section changing FSM
Parameter - advanced parameter from FSM
All Known Subinterfaces:
CreoleMarkUpOutputWriter<Parameter>
All Known Implementing Classes:
CreoleHighlighterWriter, CreoleOutputWriter
public interface MarkUpOutputWriter<Terminals extends java.lang.Enum<?>,​SectionState extends java.lang.Enum<?>,​SectionActions extends java.lang.Enum<?>,​FontState extends java.lang.Enum<?>,​FontActions extends java.lang.Enum<?>,​Parameter>

This interface describes output writers for different mark-up languages. Implementation of this interface calls from mark-up parsers to produce output, converted from source mark-up language to another language

0.0.4
